(1, 'cell line: MCF-7Xx-xXcell type: breast cancerXx-xXtreatment condition: 3h, ZNA, 30 uM', '825 Northeast 13th Street', 'Oklahoma City', 'USA', 'Immunobiology and Cancer', '', 'Oklahoma Medical Research Foundation', 'Bryan Welm Lab', 'Bryan,,Welm', '405-271-2050', '73104', 'reads were aligned to hg19 plus extended splice junctions using novoalign (2.08.01). Up to 50 alignments were reported and adapter sequences were trimmed by novoalign.Xx-xXsplice junction alignments were converted back to genomic space using the USeq (8.6.4) SamTranscriptomeParser application (default settings).Xx-xXthe final alignment files were used in the USeq (8.6.4) DefinedRegionDifferentialSeq application to generate counts per gene, variance stabilized counts, FPKM values and to determine differential expressionXx-xXGenome_build: hg19Xx-xXSupplementary_files_format_and_content: tab-delimited files contain raw read counts, FPKM values, log2ratio (DESeq) and -10*log10(adjusted p-value) (DESeq)', 0, '', 'RNA was isolated from cells using a Qiagen Rneasy kit.Xx-xXRNA libraries were prepared for sequencing using standard Illumina protocols.', 'GSM1431873', 'Illumina HiSeq 2000', 'Jul 10 2014', 'cDNA', 'transcriptomic', 'RNA-Seq', 'total RNA', 'Homo sapiens', 'GPL11154', 'BioSample: https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/biosample/SAMN02905570Xx-xXSRA: https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/sra?term=SRX648507', 'GSE59251', 'MCF-7 breast cancer cell line_3hZNA30uM-rep1', 'Public on Jul 10 2014', 'Jul 09 2014', 'NONE', '', 9606, '3hZNA30uM-rep1', 'SRA', 29453382, 32285441),
