(1, 'cell line: MDA-MB-231 breast cancer cell lineXx-xXtreatment: control siRNA-48hr', '3181 S.W. Sam Jackson Park Rd', 'Portland', 'USA', 'MMG', 'searsr@ohsu.edu', 'OHSU', '', 'Rosalie,,Sears', '5034946885', '97239-3098', 'Samples were sequenced on an Illumina HiSeq 2000 and assembled into fastq files using the CASAVA software at the OHSU Massively Parallel Sequencing Shared Resource.Xx-xXSequences were aligned to the human hg19 genome using Bowtie version 1.0.0 and seting requiring unique alignments with no more than 3 mismatches.Xx-xXTrim settings for Bowtie were selected to discard the first 4 bases, align to the next 44, and discard remaining bases from each sequence.Xx-xXAligned sequences that fell in exonic regions of RefSeq gene models were counted and normalized for sequencing depth.Xx-xXGenes that showed low normalized sequence counts for all samples were discarded from further analysis.Xx-xXGenome_build: hg19Xx-xXSupplementary_files_format_and_content: Tab-delimited .txt file containing normalized sequence counts for gene models before filtering out low expression genes.', 0, '', 'RNA was extracted from cells by Trozol reagent.Xx-xXTotal RNA was purified and reverse transcribed with oligo dT. Second strand DNA was synthesized and ligated to proprietary indexed adapters. Ligated material was amplified using Illumina genomic primers and sequenced on an Illumina GAII sequencer.', 'GSM1399410', 'Illumina HiSeq 2000', 'May 28 2014', 'cDNA', 'transcriptomic', 'RNA-Seq', 'total RNA', 'Homo sapiens', 'GPL11154', 'BioSample: https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/biosample/SAMN02800679Xx-xXSRA: https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/sra?term=SRX554352', 'GSE58008', 'MDA-MB-231 breast cancer cell line', 'Public on May 28 2014', 'May 27 2014', 'NONE', '', 9606, 'siNT', 'SRA', 13669021, 15124612),
