e/SAMN03379340Xx-xXSRA: https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/sra?term=SRX893045', 'GSE66357', 'mixture of U87 human glioma cells and MCF10a human breast cancer cells', 'Public on May 21 2015', 'Feb 27 2015', 'NONE', '', 9606, 'PS034_R2_1_480', 'SRA', 113475, 166745);
