bi.nlm.nih.gov/sra?term=SRX893219', 'GSE66357', 'MCF10a human breast cancer cells', 'Public on May 21 2015', 'Feb 27 2015', 'NONE', '', 9606, 'PS034_R2_4_128', 'SRA', 155503, 306936);
